                <note rend="inline" type="source">C.P.(Gen)Doc.1.J.13.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Article 66</hi>
                </head>
                <dateline>
                    <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-outside-research" calendar="gregorian"
                        notAfter="1946-10-15T23:59:59+01:00" notBefore="1946-07-29T00:00:00+01:00"
                        >undated</date>
                </dateline>
                <p>Add a paragraph in Article 66, reading as follows: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>“The Italian Government undertakes to restore in gold to the Greek
                            Government, within three months from the entry into force of the present
                            Treaty, the amount of 783,080 dollars advanced by Greece during the
                            occupation as a war indemnity to Italian nationals.”</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
            </div>
        </body>
